parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft timing chain can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and potentially lead to engine damage, which can compromise vehicle safety and performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the MMI screen and tail lights can compromise vehicle safety by reducing visibility and potentially leading to accidents.

symptoms: The steering wheel feels stiff or hard to turn
the power steering system fails to provide assist
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the power steering pump makes abnormal noises or leaks fluid.

the vehicle is stationary and has not been moved
